Runeforged (Jealous)		KEY:RUNEFORGED_JEALOUS		NAMEOPT:TEXT=Jealous		TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PRETYPE:1,Enhancement,Ammunition.Weapon	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against necromancy spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against necromancers and undead created by necromancy spells (not spawn or self-manifested). Absorbs three negative levels inflicted on the wielder per day.
