Runeforged (Sadistic)		KEY:RUNEFORGED_SADISTIC		NAMEOPT:TEXT=Sadistic		TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PRETYPE:1,Enhancement,Ammunition.Weapon	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against abjuration spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against abjurers and any creatures with an active abjuration spell effect. Shrouds wielder in a mock magic aura. When targeted with a dispelling effect, the effect targets mock aura instead, once every 24 hours.
Runeforged (Parasitic)		KEY:RUNEFORGED_PARASITIC	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Parasitic		TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PRETYPE:1,Enhancement,Ammunition.Weapon	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against enchantment spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against enchanters and against creatures that are charmed, dominated, or under another creature's magic control. Automatically dispels enchantment effect on a struck creature with such an active effect (CL 13). On success, heals wielder 6d6. Excess hitpoints are gained as temporary hitpoints for 1 hour.
